  When working with cameras, you have to assign them to a
  <strong>
   view port
  </strong>
  for them to be "active" and display anything. These view ports are numbered from 0 to 7 and can be changed and positioned using different variable arrays and functions, and you can also check to see which one is currently drawing or which camera is currently attached to it.
  
  
